National Fuel adds Chevron NJ gas customers . National Fuel Resources Inc said Tuesday it acquired the rights to all of Chevron Corp ' s New Jersey retail natural gas sales contracts for undisclosed terms . The company ' s National Fuel Gas Co subsidiary also said it was reviewing proposed residential pilot programs filed by New Jersey natural gas utilities . Under the programs , residential gas customers can select their natural gas supplier on a competitive basis . National Fuel said it expected to participate in at least one pilot program in New Jersey . " The addition of the Chevron customer base to our existing New Jersey operations strengthens our market position as one of the larger retail ( natural ) gas marketers operating in the state of New Jersey , " the company said in a statement . - - Jim Brumm 212 - 859 - 1710 
